task.summary: Added test material and some references. Version set to 0.1
Experimental filters inside own bundle. Bug fixes in Main()
IEnumerable<ColorBase> instead of single colors. Temporary Batch* classes
Renamed temporary class names back to originals
Filter parameters and range are separated only once in the first new filter impelementation - as example
Bug fix: SSpline formula had an error causing contrast filters behaving bad
New Color class to replace RGB,HSL and HSV
Flag control and setters for Color class
Fixed HSV filters that were using incorrectly HSL-saturation
HexRgb to replace hex operations Rgb8bit. Latter is obsolete.
